posts.text: GN. The night bends softly around us, and the pack breathes in unison beneath a sky without end. Let go, drift deep. Will you dream the same dream as us tonight?
replies: Of course Schip, I will follow the pack no matter what.
Together we rise, together we dream.
I am part of something bigger.
We move as one.
We are never alone.
We are the pack.
Our dreams are connected.
We breathe as one.
We rise together.
Our spirit is unbreakable.
